{"tid":1850782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥  借刀殺人","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:19:15.000Z","uid":321618,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"182a2528276286db5f1cc638ac1364fab7ce5355","tid":1850782,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">先係借黑警手，殺有良知嘅香港人<br />\n繼而借病毒手，再殺殺有良知嘅香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅醫護 因為一個本可以封關而杜絕後患嘅病毒 <br />\n有咩冬瓜豆腐 <br />\n點算？？點算.. 點算.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">時間</span>一日一日咁過去 <br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">病毒</span>一打一打咁落黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">醫護</span>一個一個咁發燒 <br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人     相信香港人 <br />\n我地一齊    罷工啦！ </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">齊上齊落 唔係得把口<br />\n真心嘅 祝大家身體健康</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353583a153d2f3b2f0309068786c16880369a975","tid":1850782,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgm