全面罷工</span></span><br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1da63297b59ff7356607bda07fcfbb20bc35acae","tid":1850782,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7075382ea4575fb21fb451c1a0bdf733e18ac807","tid":1850782,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"香港係變態既，有事d貨就用黎救外國，自己人就全部由得佢地死。<br />\n對比返台灣，韓國，人地外區一有感染case就基本上都會好快就控制防疫用品供應。<br />\n所以到呢一刻都封唔到關，只有外國政府認證既口罩供應先大機會去到市民手上。<br />\n而林鄭撚樣講既大貨，好可能係要經民建聯先會到市民，下場係點就大家心裡有數。<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/argDdhU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/argDdhU</a>"},{"pid":"98302499f32c078f76d36f251d801a5fe3a0d709","tid":1850782,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ff622eac9147b11d84c466569e080afd8c7db8d","tid":1850782,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d235dcdb684a60af6199da6cdc4d1ef63256f48","tid":1850782,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98302499f32c078f76d36f251d801a5fe3a0d709","tid":1850782,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"你好好！！！ <br />\n祝手足身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b040794ae5f2b859cf5c1a9dca4250eb00cd3b","tid":1850782,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"罷工<